_Main::saveAllTabsHidden() in favor of Tribe__Settings_Manager::save_all_tabs_hidden()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; Tribe__Events__Main::setNetworkOptions() in favor of Tribe__Settings_Manager::set_network_options()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; Tribe__Events__Main::setNotice() in favor of Tribe__Notices::set_notice()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; Tribe__Events__Main::truncate() in favor of tribe_events_get_the_excerpt()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; tribe_event_beginning_of_day() in favor of tribe_beginning_of_day()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; tribe_event_end_of_day() in favor of tribe_end_of_day()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; tribe_event_format_date() in favor of tribe_format_date()</li>\n<li>Deprecated &#8211; tribe_events_the_notices() in favor of tribe_the_notices()</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.x and previous</h4>\n<p>For release notes from the 3.x and older lifecycles, see our <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/category/products/release-notes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">full historical release notes</a>.</p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2685:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Month View with Hover\"></a><p>Month View with Hover</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Events List Widget\"></a><p>Events List Widget</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Mobile Month View\"></a><p>Mobile Month View</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"CSV Importer\"></a><p>CSV Importer</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Month View\"></a><p>Month View</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"List View\"></a><p>List View</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Day View\"></a><p>Day View</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Single Event\"></a><p>Single Event</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Event Editor\"></a><p>Event Editor</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Events Admin Listing\"></a><p>Events Admin Listing</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"General Settings\"></a><p>General Settings</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=1679210\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=1679210\" alt=\"Display Settings\"></a><p>Display Settings</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14112:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Well Designed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akanning\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a70c8048b721f08fa99fadcfdcefb15f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a70c8048b721f08fa99fadcfdcefb15f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akanning\" class=\"reviewer-name\">akanning</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 29, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is exactly what our organization needed for our internal website. It was easy to set up and even easier to maintain. A must have for any WordPress site!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No Google Calendar Support (Free Version)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brokoliweb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7020781a367b03856dcf22aeda98ff24?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7020781a367b03856dcf22aeda98ff24?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brokoliweb\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brokoliweb</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 28, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had the impression it supports google calendar But NO Google Calendar support unless you buy it.. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works right out the box. Easy to set up</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tuty-voa\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99b6e4ac0687df4607b5f76cea7be7e5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99b6e4ac0687df4607b5f76cea7be7e5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tuty-voa\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tuty VOA</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 27, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Excellent plugin. The free version has met all of our needs. Thank you.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin! Great Support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/colinjswinney\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af6c9acfdc34f86a8a8131ee49144a5f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af6c9acfdc34f86a8a8131ee49144a5f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/colinjswinney\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ColinJSwinney</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 26, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I built a custom theme with Roots/Sage and this plugin.  Good documentation, and great support when I had an issue with adding the calendar to the homepage.  They had been aware of the problem when I contacted, and they emailed me this morning as soon as the fix was released.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Free Event Tool</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nicklouckes\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f94d7353246573e71b3b0035310c7130?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f94d7353246573e71b3b0035310c7130?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nicklouckes\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nick.louckes</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 23, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is easy to use, and has all the necessary tools to get the job done - for free. Great plugin - well written. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">So much more than I need</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frogstar42\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82783d96d0628d3ff1bd635d7de6d9a8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82783d96d0628d3ff1bd635d7de6d9a8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frogstar42\" class=\"reviewer-name\">frogstar42</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 21, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We started using this plugin years ago to display a basic monthly event calendar but every year I look at the manual and discover new ways to use it. I charge the client for upgraded features. (shhhh)  This thing just does SO MUCH.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pretty pleased with this one</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/okieman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b224fbea1bf29699912a80e28859fdaf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b224fbea1bf29699912a80e28859fdaf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/okieman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">okieman</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 19, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We purchased The Events Calendar PRO (Modern Tribe) for our church site tulsaunity.com. It has worked well and no breakage or other hassles. Our office manager uses it constantly without any help from me; the webmaster. We recently qualified for a discount they occasionally offer to non-profits, so now we have the latest and greatest. Well done, tribes-persons.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Any serious developer should avoid using this</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m_disseny\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8e48442c5126b7b2581509f6ac3ed79?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8e48442c5126b7b2581509f6ac3ed79?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m_disseny\" class=\"reviewer-name\">m_disseny</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using the pro version in a couple of projects during 4 years and still suffering its consequences. Low quality programming, bad performance, lack of support (lots of gentle but nonsense words, thank you Barry) and security vulnerabilities that\'s what I got after purchasing this plugin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stacyvh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3200df05d58f25ddbcd0857e72ab7d7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3200df05d58f25ddbcd0857e72ab7d7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stacyvh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">StacyVH</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 16, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The Events Calendar is great! Highly recommend. Quick, intuitive set up yet many ways to customize. I am recommending it in a speech I\'m presenting at WordPress Grand Rapids.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">awesome!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p clas